Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:17.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}小さな思い出たち
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:23.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}両手いっぱい抱えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:28.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}あなただけ 想ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:34.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}そんな時間(とき)がうれしい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:39.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}どんなに離れても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:45.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}愛する気持ちはいつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:51.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}あなたの隣にそっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:57.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}寄り添っている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.23,0:01:05.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}そう 決して終わることのない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:10.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}本当の愛 見つけたから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:16.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}「ずっとずっとそばにいます」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.73,0:01:21.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}誓ったあおい空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是有必要确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,第十一话 ～月光～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 蒂娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小茧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是有什么事瞒着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,隐瞒的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好像…没有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 小茧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,之前在温泉度假村的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人在电话里说要回美国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜 真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…不…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜学长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,学长？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:02:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子痛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为是什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回美国？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在想什么哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你才会被别人看成小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你 那个时候 的确…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 那个时候的确那么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但那是年末探亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,探…探亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你回了日本以后 听力是不是生锈了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,说到底是你的英语口音太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,找借口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 不要吓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,薰 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我买了新的数字相机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一直很想要的呢 蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,用这个拍很多大家的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,回去之后 就能给爸爸妈妈看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那 那个…蒂娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,拍照片没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可是这个样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,说到拍照 还是cosplay好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不对吧 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,千香无所谓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 加油 蒂娜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么只有我是河马！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为只剩下这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那么先从房东小姐开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,房东小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,笑一个笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得有点难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好 要拍咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,笑容笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要尽情的拍咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,太性感了 管理员小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 接下来摆个母豹的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,母 母豹？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,nice母豹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 等等 薰 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就全了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜 回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,早说了我不是失败狗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜 要回去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,薰 等一下 再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜再有一点就通关了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,薰 这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,best timing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 蒂娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很好的风景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,来这里就是想拍一张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我呢 很喜欢这里的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,夕阳渐渐下沉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,和我以前住的地方很像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,以前住的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,九州岛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,美国
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在这里没什么好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因为一直是寂寞时才来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想得在这里留下个美好回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,听了那些话后 我可担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那些话？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,回美国的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,当真了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,以蒂娜的作风 可没法当作笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,以前也这么做过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,发现纸板箱！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一起滑吧 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要吗 蒂娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,来呀来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 真那你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那么开始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,变冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我回房间去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再突然走掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 大家好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这里又不像那里那么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始就是这么说好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只在日本待到大学毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的 我会回美国去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能说得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就要分别了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要是对薰说了 那我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就再也不是现在的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢薰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,却无法继续在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我必须要笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,必须要一直笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,和大家一起笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一起制造好多的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜欢大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,妙子姐姐 快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没 没事吧 妙子小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,妙子 千香 过个好年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是 各位也过个好年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,妙子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,千香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,说回来 蒂娜什么时候回去?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在稍微多待一会儿就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,妙子 千香 byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧 千香？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,郁女的也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就在明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,房东小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,要喝茶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次烤了芝士蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道合不合蒂娜小姐的口味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话 请尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,拍了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,房东小姐也看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是那时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这样真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈都会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这 这个 是什么时候拍的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈一定会吃惊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这个可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛 又不会怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 蒂娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不饿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得明明只是妙子和千香不在 却觉得如此安静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得就像少了重要的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,妙子 千香都是重要的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不在的话果真会很寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚喝酒 喝完了闹个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,其实只是想喝酒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再突然走掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,薰 醒着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没可能还醒着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,和你说点话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 因为这是我最后的任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再待在日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,必须回美国去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大学毕业就要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样和爸爸妈妈约好后来的日本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,回去了的话 大概 不会再…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,薰…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,想更多…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,更多地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想再制造更多更多和薰的快乐回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:18:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,然后也想让薰更多更多地了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不想回去啊 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,想在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,从今以后…一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我…对薰…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,对薰…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,房东小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这么早在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是这个时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,房东小姐每天都起这么早吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜小姐 难道是今天回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是很早的航班 也不想大家为了送我而早起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,房东小姐 不好意思 郁女就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,难得回去一次 必须多孝敬孝敬父母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,也许会待长点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,过个好年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,房东小姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,（谢谢）
